snippet.title: Full Void - Official Console Release Window and Accolade Trailer
snippet.description:
Full Void will be available on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X/S, and Xbox One in September 2023. Additionally, Full Void is coming to Evercade in October 2023, and it is available now on PC. Watch the latest trailer for Full Void for another look at the creepy world of this 2D cinematic puzzle platformer game.

Full Void is set in a despotic future where AI is running amok and keeping humankind oppressed under their full tyranny. You will uncover the story of a young teenager who’s all alone in a hellish landscape controlled by multiple hostile rogue AIs.
